title: [FINAL PROPOSAL] Pukenza
body:
tl;dr
Pukenzas have passed the preliminary proposal phase! Thanks everyone! We want to give all Doods the opportunity to claim a free (+ gas) Pukenza generative artwork by @L3xc

Background on Pukenza
A member of the Doodles community, Lim (a.k.a. @L3xc), is a very talented generative artist and developer at WestCoastNFT, the company that did the smart contract work for Doodles. Inspired by Tyler Hobbs’ article about Flow Field and Fidenza, he decided to play with those concepts and combine them with the Doodles color palette to create a really cool generative art piece called “Rainbow Puke over the Flow Field,” now lovingly known as “Pukenza.” The original proposal for Pukenza was so popular and received so much support that we passed the preliminary Snapshot with flying pukey colors! Since then, Lim has continued to work hard at developing the art, refining the outputs, and doing all the little technical things that need to be done in order for us to all be able to receive our beautiful Pukenzas!

Why Pukenza?
This art is awesome and it would be a nice little treat to Doodle holders whilst rewarding an artist that is deeply involved with the Doodles community!

How will this be delivered?
@L3xc and @WestCoastNFT will deliver the Pukenza via https://degenartclub.com/

Wen Pukenza mint:
4-6 Weeks

This time will allow for:
- Polishing the algorithm for the generative art
- Testing outputs
- Smart contract + website preparation

You can find frequent updates on the project in Lim's Degen Art Club Discord server: https://discord.gg/csh7FGjcMm

Did you vote on the preliminary snapshot? If you did, you can claim a fun Pukenza Voter POAP which will also make you eligible to enter a raffle to win one of ten custom Pukenzas by @L3xc himself!

More info on the POAP and raffle here: https://forum.doodles.app/t/poaps-for-votes/1274

Budget: Stacks

Cost: 4.20 ETH total
- 3ETH to L3xc for artwork (address: L3xc.eth)
- 1.2 ETH to WestcoastNFT for smart contract development + contract deployment gas fee + website development (address: 0xwest)
- 7.5% royalty on secondary sales
- 5% going to L3xc
- 2.5% going to Doodlebank

Accountability:
- funds will be transferred into gnosis multisig with tulip/burnt/poopie as cosigners in a 4/5
policy
- funds will be paid out on delivery of completed timeline found in this final proposal

Links:
New proposal discussion: https://forum.doodles.app/t/pukenza-airdrop-for-doods/367
Preliminary proposal (snapshot):
https://snapshot.org/#/doodles.eth/proposal/0x0c8179316680c90dc6f7ef131b3e4c21c7eb42e502c7273bac9581e8e2bf95e4
Thanks for reading this, and thank you for the continued support
- Jer #276
